---
// Attribution strip, directly under every hero. Non-negotiable, every page.
// The wording is fixed. Do not edit it.
---

<div class="attribution">
  <p class="container">
    Founded &amp; hosted by Nadia · Yoga led by senior teacher Monica of YogaMorphic
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .attribution {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-deep);
  }

  .attribution p {
    margin: 0;
    padding-block: 0.85rem;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sage-dark);
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
